div.div: feat: add instructions for quest logging
Closed #49 How did uploamy run on your overlay
Commented on #49 How did uploamy run on your overlay

This is the way I personally do it:
Go to Mezeporta, load the Overlay. Press Shift+F1 , go to Quest Log tab. Go to Settings tab inside the Quest Log tab, press Select Game Folder button Navigate to the folder where your mhf.exe (the game) resides, select it and press Select folder. press the Select Custom Folder for quest Runs Database. Navigate to any folder (I made a database folder in the game folder), give the file a name (I named mine MHFZ_Overlay.sqlite), press Save. Toggle Quest Logging Press the green Save button at the bottom in order for the overlay settings to be saved. Restart the Overlay. Do a run and once you are back at hub, check if the run is there by going into Config -> Quest Log -> Section Most Recent
